IRC bot that uses POE::Component::IRC::State and Net::Twitter::Lite.
It tweets all uppercase lines that contain a user-defined 'trigger'.

The install script uses local::lib and cpanm (App::cpanminus) to set
up a user-local Perl module library and install the needed modules.

It is specific to my shell/hosting provider. ( The '@followers' command
anyway. )

'twircer' is just here for storage, 'install' does all the work.
( Not that this is intended to be used by anyone. )
